FRIDAY, SEPTEMBER 21, MOSELEY’S –ON- THE- CHARLES,

 50 Bridge St.,   DEDHAM  (Exit 16A off Rte. 128/95, Rte. 109 East)

www.MoseleysontheCharles.com . HUGE dance floor, pizza, desserts…non-stop dance music…by the best DJ in the business…BRIAN MILLIGAN.

      HUNDREDS AND HUNDREDS AND HUNDREDS OF SINGLES.

Free door prizes, SPLIT-THE-POT raffle, and play our popular CARD-MATCHING game for additional prizes.

Proper business dress recommended.

*******************************************************************

SATURDAY, SEPTEMBER 22,  CHRISTINA’S GRAND Ballroom

2 Washington St., Rte.1 northbound, FOXBORO. (508)668-7200.

Non-stop dance music by our most popular DJ, JOHN BAZZ. Come EARLY if you want a table. HUNDREDS AND HUNDREDS AND HUNDREDS OF SINGLES.

Free door prizes, SPLIT-THE-POT raffle, and play our popular CARD-MATCHING game for additional prizes.

Proper business dress recommended.

GOT A DATE SATURDAY NIGHT? Bring your date to dance and meet your friends and your date will be admitted FREE.
